Package org.eclipse.actf.visualization.engines.blind.html.ui.elementViewer

This package includes interfaces and factory class for HTML Element viewer.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IElementViewerAccessKeyInfo
    Interface to store accesskey information
    IElementViewerIdInfo
    Interface to store ID information
    IElementViewerInfoProvider
    Interface to add information to element information viewer.
    IElementViewerManager
    IElementViewerManager is used to control element information viewer
    IHighlightElementListener
    Interface to highlight corresponding position of selected item in visualization result.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ElementViewerManagerFactory
    Factory for IElementViewerManager that manages element information viewer in blind visualization mode
